query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS firebase_topic_subscriptions (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  topic_id INT NOT NULL,
  device_token_id INT NOT NULL,
  subscribed_at BIGINT NOT NULL,
  INDEX idx_topic_sub_topic (topic_id),
  INDEX idx_topic_sub_device (device_token_id)
);
